    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Facilities designed for the creation and distribution of power derived from wind, where turbines convert the kinetic energy of wind into mechanical or electrical energy that can be used for power.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
